  "id": "ka0aT000000OMFVQA4",
  "articleNumber": "000001592",
  "title": "Technical requirements on Computers refurbishment",
  "urlName": "Technical-requirements-on-Computers-refurbishment",
  "url": "https://backmarket.my.site.com/ssc/s/article/Technical-requirements-on-Computers-refurbishment",
  "language": "en_GB",
  "lastPublishedDate": "2026-03-02T15:42:18.000Z",
  "topics": [],
  "bodyHtml": "<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">To ensure the highest quality and customer satisfaction, all laptops and computers must undergo comprehensive refurbishment, including thorough testing of hardware and software components, meticulous cleaning to remove dust and debris, and secure packaging to protect the devices during transit. Adhering to these standards guarantees that each product meets our rigorous performance and aesthetic criteria.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>Note:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">OEM battery charge limiting features (Dell Battery Charge Configuration, HP Battery Health Manager, Lenovo Conservation Mode) artificially cap Full Charge Capacity in Windows battery reports, leading to perceived “low battery health”.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">For any laptop, the battery might be reported as 80% or less, it may be a saving feature (not a defect). This intentional cap helps extend long‑term battery lifespan by limiting the maximum charge. If you want the battery to reach full capacity, disable Energy Saving / Battery Conservation / Battery Protection mode (name varies by brand). Then charge the laptop again and check the battery level.</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Recommended Action - Mandatory Pre-Shipment: </span></strong><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\"></span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Disable ALL charge limits via respective BIOS/Vantage settings</span></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;color: #000000;\">Verify 100% charge capability</span></li></ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Jump to :</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"#h_84137417334621739805967351\" target=\"_self\">Gaming Computers</a></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"#h_75123950141561739805988172\" target=\"_self\">Gaming Laptops</a></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"#h_56181411846031739805997939\" target=\"_self\">Office Laptops</a></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"#h_85401941452731739806005986\" target=\"_self\">Desktop Computers</a></span></li><li style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"#h_19999062956811739806013556\" target=\"_self\">Notebooks &amp; Ultrabooks</a></span></li></ul>\n<h2 id=\"h_84137417334621739805967351\"><a id=\"H2\" target=\"_blank\"></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Gaming Computers</span></h2>\n<table dir=\"ltr\" style=\"table-layout: fixed;font-size: 10pt;font-family: Arial;width: 0px;border-collapse: collapse;border-style: none;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><colgroup><col width=\"251\"></col><col width=\"370\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Refurbishing &amp; Repairs</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Replace faulty components (GPU, CPU, RAM, SSD/HDD, PSU, cooling). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Apply high-quality thermal paste. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Upgrade BIOS &amp; firmware. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure PSU meets power requirements. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Secure all cables and internal components.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Testing &amp; Performance</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Full POST test. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Stress-test CPU/GPU with Cinebench, FutureMark, 3DMark (30 min). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Memory diagnostics (MemTest86). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Check storage health (CrystalDiskInfo). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Verify motherboard ports (USB, HDMI, Ethernet, Wi-Fi). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Benchmark gaming performance.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cleaning &amp; Aesthetics</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Remove dust with compressed air. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Deep clean case, remove scratches if possible. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Secure all internal components. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Replace or clean thermal pads. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure no rattling parts inside.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Packaging &amp; Shipping</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Use anti-static bags for internal components. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Secure GPU &amp; CPU cooler with protective padding. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Use foam inserts/custom padding inside the case. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ship in a sturdy, double-walled box.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2></h2>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 id=\"h_75123950141561739805988172\"><a id=\"H2\" target=\"_blank\"></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Gaming Laptops</span></h2>\n<table dir=\"ltr\" style=\"table-layout: fixed;font-size: 10pt;font-family: Arial;width: 0px;border-collapse: collapse;border-style: none;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><colgroup><col width=\"251\"></col><col width=\"324\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Refurbishing &amp; Repairs</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Replace faulty parts (GPU, RAM, SSD/HDD, cooling system, battery). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Apply new thermal paste to CPU &amp; GPU. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Upgrade BIOS &amp; firmware.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Check &amp; replace worn-out keyboard, trackpad, and hinges. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure battery health is above 80%/85%.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Testing &amp; Performance</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Full POST test. - Stress-test CPU/GPU. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Battery health test (charge cycles &amp; capacity). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Verify RGB, keyboard, trackpad, webcam, and speakers. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Check all ports (USB, HDMI, audio, charging). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Benchmark gaming performance.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cleaning &amp; Aesthetics</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Deep clean chassis, keyboard, screen, and fans. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Clean screen to remove smudges. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure no loose hinges or damaged frame. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Remove dust from vents and cooling system.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Packaging &amp; Shipping</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Use shockproof packaging. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Include original charger or compatible replacement. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Label package as FRAGILE.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2></h2>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 id=\"h_56181411846031739805997939\"><a id=\"H2\" target=\"_blank\"></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Office Laptops</span></h2>\n<table dir=\"ltr\" style=\"table-layout: fixed;font-size: 10pt;font-family: Arial;width: 0px;border-collapse: collapse;border-style: none;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><colgroup><col width=\"251\"></col><col width=\"351\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Refurbishing &amp; Repairs</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Replace faulty parts (RAM, SSD/HDD, battery, keyboard, screen). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Apply new thermal paste to the CPU. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Upgrade BIOS &amp; firmware. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure battery health is above 80%. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Check &amp; replace worn-out ports, hinges, and fans.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Testing &amp; Performance</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Full POST test. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Battery health test (capacity &gt;80%). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Stress-test CPU.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Verify keyboard, trackpad, and webcam. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Test all ports (USB, HDMI, Ethernet, audio, charging).</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cleaning &amp; Aesthetics</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Deep clean keyboard, screen, chassis, and ports. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Clean screen to remove fingerprints. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Remove dust from fans and vents. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure no loose parts or hinge issues.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Packaging &amp; Shipping</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Use padded laptop sleeves &amp; anti-static bags. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Wrap in bubble wrap &amp; ship in a secure laptop box. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Include original charger or compatible replacement. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Label package as FRAGILE.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2></h2>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 id=\"h_85401941452731739806005986\"><a id=\"H2\" target=\"_blank\"></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Desktop Computers</span></h2>\n<table dir=\"ltr\" style=\"table-layout: fixed;font-size: 10pt;font-family: Arial;width: 0px;border-collapse: collapse;border-style: none;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><colgroup><col width=\"251\"></col><col width=\"299\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Refurbishing &amp; Repairs</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Replace defective parts (CPU, RAM, SSD/HDD, PSU). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Apply thermal paste to the CPU. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Upgrade BIOS &amp; firmware.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Secure all internal connections. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure PSU is stable and noise-free.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Testing &amp; Performance</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Full POST test. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Stress-test CPU. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Memory diagnostics (MemTest86). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Check storage health. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Verify all ports (USB, HDMI, Ethernet, Wi-Fi). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Boot test with pre-installed OS.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cleaning &amp; Aesthetics</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Clean dust from internal &amp; external parts. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure no major scratches or dents.</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Secure cables and connectors.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Packaging &amp; Shipping</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Use anti-static bags for internal components. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Secure PSU &amp; motherboard to avoid movement. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Use protective padding inside the case</span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ship in a sturdy, well-cushioned box.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2></h2>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 id=\"h_19999062956811739806013556\"><a id=\"H2\" target=\"_blank\"></a><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Notebooks &amp; Ultrabooks</span></h2>\n<table dir=\"ltr\" style=\"table-layout: fixed;font-size: 10pt;font-family: Arial;width: 0px;border-collapse: collapse;border-style: none;\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><colgroup><col width=\"251\"></col><col width=\"251\"></col></colgroup><tbody><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Refurbishing &amp; Repairs</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Replace faulty parts (RAM, SSD, battery, keyboard, screen). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Upgrade BIOS &amp; firmware. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Apply new thermal paste to the CPU. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure battery health is above 85%. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Verify hinge and chassis integrity.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Testing &amp; Performance</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Full POST test. - Battery health test (capacity &gt;85%). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Verify keyboard, trackpad, webcam, fingerprint reader (if applicable). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Test all ports (USB-C, Thunderbolt, HDMI, audio, charging). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Boot test with pre-installed OS.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Cleaning &amp; Aesthetics</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Deep clean keyboard, screen, and chassis. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Clean screen </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Ensure no visible wear on hinges. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Remove dust from internal components.</span></td></tr><tr style=\"height: 21px;\"><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-left: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;font-weight: bold;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Packaging &amp; Shipping</span></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"border-right: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(0, 0, 0);overflow: hidden;padding: 2px 3px;vertical-align: middle;white-space: normal;overflow-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Use padded sleeves &amp; anti-static bags. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Wrap in bubble wrap &amp; ship in a secure, lightweight box. </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Include USB-C/thunderbolt charger (if required). </span><br><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">- Label as FRAGILE.</span></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p> </p>"
}